<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>ومرتد بطرّة ... مسدلة <span class="c2">«٣»</span> الرفارف<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>كأنّها مسبلة <span class="c2">«٤»</span> ... من زرد مضاعف <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
